### Test EmailTriggerReport Filtered API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5037/api/EmailTriggerReport

### 1. Get filtered reports with strategy name filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?strategyName=promotional&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get filtered reports with date range filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?firstEmailSentFrom=2024-01-01&firstEmailSentTo=2024-12-31&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get filtered reports with numeric filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?minTotalEmails=100&minDeliveredCount=50&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 4. Get filtered reports with sorting (descending by total emails)
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?sortBy=TotalEmails&sortDirection=desc&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 5. Get filtered reports with multiple filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?strategyName=newsletter&minTotalEmails=50&sortBy=OpenedCount&sortDirection=desc&pageNumber=1&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### 6. Get filtered reports with invalid date range (should return 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?firstEmailSentFrom=2024-12-31&firstEmailSentTo=2024-01-01
Accept: application/json

### 7. Get filtered reports with invalid page number (should return 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?pageNumber=0
Accept: application/json

### 8. Get filtered reports with too large page size (should return 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?pageSize=2000
Accept: application/json

### 9. Get filtered reports with all available sort fields
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?sortBy=StrategyName&pageSize=3
Accept: application/json

### 10. Get filtered reports sorted by DeliveredCount
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?sortBy=DeliveredCount&sortDirection=desc&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### 11. Get filtered reports sorted by OpenedCount
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?sortBy=OpenedCount&sortDirection=desc&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### 12. Get filtered reports sorted by ClickedCount
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?sortBy=ClickedCount&sortDirection=desc&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### 13. Get filtered reports with complex filtering
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?minTotalEmails=75&minOpenedCount=25&minClickedCount=10&sortBy=TotalEmails&sortDirection=desc&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 14. Get filtered reports with no filters (all data)
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### 15. Test pagination (page 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/filtered?pageNumber=2&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json
